    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Cross-project registry</strong> — <code>~/.stack/projects.json</code>
      tracks every <code>.stack.toml</code> on the machine;{" "}
      <code>stack doctor --all</code> runs healthchecks across all of them.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>97 tests</strong> passing across the core, CLI, and MCP
